class_notes: Online Asynchronous with on-campus intensives on Feb 1-3 and March 17-19.
course_description: This course focuses on advanced assessment competencies and primary healthcare for low-moderate risk neonates and older infants up to age 2. Students explore collaboration practice models and innovative faculty/student practice models for resuscitation, stabilization and advanced procedural skills.
